<h2>About English Bulldogs</h2>

<p>
English Bulldogs are one of the most recognizable dog breeds in the world. 
They are known for their wrinkled faces, muscular build, and lovable personalities.
Despite their tough appearance, bulldogs are extremely affectionate and loyal companions.
</p>

<p>
They are great family dogs and love being around people. Bulldogs are calm, friendly,
and often very funny because of their stubborn but charming personalities.
</p>

