<h2>Bulldog Care Tips</h2>

<ul>
<li>Short daily walks are perfect for bulldogs.</li>
<li>Clean their facial wrinkles regularly to prevent infections.</li>
<li>Avoid overheating — bulldogs don't handle heat well.</li>
<li>Feed high-quality dog food in controlled portions.</li>
<li>Regular vet visits help maintain their health.</li>
</ul>

